这里，我们依然没有定义 copy constructor, copy assignment operator, or destructor。 
All our members are stored by value and are therefore well behaved on a program level under the default semantics. (Some people would argue that the introduction of a virtual function should always be accompanied by the declaration of a virtual destructor. But doing that would buy us nothing in this case.) 这里存疑哈，trivail desctructor是nonvirtual的，如果派生类确实需要在desctrctor中执行一些操作，而 delete p将调用 Point的trivial destructor，这是不对的
